videos.headline: Aliyah Boston fake turns into mid-range jumper for 2
videos.description: As Brea Beal cuts backdoor, Aliyah Boston fakes a pass leaving her wide open for the easy bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Aliyah Boston fake turns into mid-range jumper for 2) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Myah Selland makes nice pass in transition for 2
videos.description: Myah Selland races down the court to make a slick pass to Madison Mathiowetz for an easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Myah Selland makes nice pass in transition for 2) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Laeticia Amihere steals the rock then dumps it off in the paint for 2
videos.description: After Laeticia Amihere makes a defensive stop on the opposing side, she strides down the court and makes a slick pass near the cup for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Laeticia Amihere steals the rock then dumps it off in the paint for 2) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brooklyn Meyer makes smart pass at the rim for 2
videos.description: Brooklyn Meyer uses her great passing skills to make an excellent assist to Tori Nelson for 2.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Brooklyn Meyer makes smart pass at the rim for 2) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zia Cooke makes steal then finishes for 2 on the other end
videos.description: Zia Cooke rips Haleigh Timmer then scores in transition to put the Gamecocks up by 13.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Zia Cooke makes steal then finishes for 2 on the other end) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brea Beal's hustle on defense leads to layup in the paint
videos.description: Brea Beal makes great defensive play and is rewarded by Kierra Fletcher's assist.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Brea Beal's hustle on defense leads to layup in the paint) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Myah Selland hits corner 3 to cut South Dakota State's deficit to just 8
videos.description: South Dakota State's Myah Selland lights it up from 3 after a slick find from Tori Nelson.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Myah Selland hits corner 3 to cut South Dakota State's deficit to just 8) 2022/12/16 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zia Cooke buries 3 to put South Carolina up by 13
videos.description: The Gamecocks excellent movement on the offensive end leads to corner 3 by Zia Cooke.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Zia Cooke buries 3 to put South Carolina up by 13) 2022/12/16 ESHEET
